channel.description:
Welcome all today ill be releasing my client.
What is in the client?:
[ul][*]474 Items [*]474 Non-Playing characters [*]474 Graphics [*]474 Animations [*]474 Objects [*]459 Gameframe[/ul]
Things that you need to do:! -You need to pack the anim files inside of the cache -You need to pack the Models inside of the cache
Download link: client still has the 317 models in them while there not needed. Client: [url=http://www.upload.ee/files/625895/Swat_s_Client_2010.rar.html]UPLOAD.EE - Download Swat_s_Client_2010.rar[/url]
Add these in the cache folder or pack them inside of the cache. Anims: [url=http://www.upload.ee/files/625891/anim.rar.html]UPLOAD.EE - Download anim.rar[/url]
474 Models: [url=http://www.upload.ee/files/625902/models.rar.html]UPLOAD.EE - Download models.rar[/url]
There should be no errors or anti leech, dont forget to change the npc bits to [COLOR="Red"]16 [/COLOR] not 14
There is one thing i forgot to add inside the class7 [CODE] private final void method175(int i, Class25 class25, Class11 class11, int j, int k, int l, int i1, boolean flag, int j1) { if(i1 == 15552|| i1 == 26923||i1 == 2396||i1==24299||i1==21304)return;[/CODE] replace that
EXTRA INFORMATION: Suite still works. Everything can be copied from the client, and the .idx and dats taken from the client port is 43595 not 43594 [COLOR="Red"][SIZE="6"]HAPPY LEECHING![/SIZE][/COLOR] ScreenShots: [img]http://i45.tinypic.com/w89pbo.jpg[/img] [img]http://i48.tinypic.com/2uztmxg.jpg[/img] [img]http://i47.tinypic.com/315l8gj.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/2gwwffq.jpg[/img] [img]http://i48.tinypic.com/29mu6nr.jpg[/img] [img]http://i46.tinypic.com/t55c00.jpg[/img] [img]http://i49.tinypic.com/t56gz9.jpg[/img] [img]http://i47.tinypic.com/2i24gt3.jpg[/img] [img]http://i45.tinypic.com/153xmo6.jpg[/img] [img]http://i46.tinypic.com/11j3hmt.jpg[/img] [img]http://i48.tinypic.com/2nvbk1h.jpg[/img] [img]http://i49.tinypic.com/29fdlhc.jpg[/img] [img]http://i49.tinypic.com/oscw1c.jpg[/img] [img]http://i48.tinypic.com/whfu6q.jpg[/img] [img]http://i48.tinypic.com/30c0u2w.jpg[/img] [img]http://i48.tinypic.com/wj7zm1.jpg[/img]
